dct_title_s: Relative Positions of Present and Former Pierhead and Bulkhead Lines on East Side of Delaware River between Erie Street and Federal Street in the City of Camden
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Penn Street to Elm Street in Camden along the Delaware River. Map shows the granted lands along the Delaware River and the various property owners, as well as the pierhead and bulkhead lines.
